1558073.title: 501 Seventh Avenue - West 37th Street
1558073.folder: 501 Seventh Avenue - West 37th Street, Manhattan, NY

712431f.text:
204 (clearance) and 206 (3-story structure) West 37th Street, adjoining and west of the S.W. corner of Seventh Ave., showing mainly the space where a 3-story frame structure stood. This in conjunction with the standing structures form a portion of the present site of the 24-story Garment Centre Building. This set consists of a negative and a positive.
January 12, 1920.
P. M. Demarest.
0ift of Albert A. Volk Co.
